snippet.title: Dakar18 FeaturesTrailer
snippet.description:
Portuguese development studio and Rally enthusiasts Bigmoon Entertainment today revealed a new trailer for the upcoming world’s first real Rally Raid Simulation Dakar 18, which will release on PlayStation®4, Xbox One and PC 25th of September 2018. 

More information about Dakar 18 can be found here on https://www.facebook.com/dakarthegame and http://www.dakarthegame.com, information about the Dakar Rally is available here: http://www.dakar.com
